rows.label: qev086701_MSG0002
rows.name:
With Luxaar out of the picture,
the Ganglion have been pretty quiet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086701_MSG0003
rows.name: You make peace sound like a bad thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086701_MSG0004
rows.name:
But if you're looking for something to do,
I've got a job for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086701_MSG0005
rows.name: Ooh, a mission straight from the boss![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086701_MSG0006
rows.name: Tatsu do it! And anything else Elma need.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086701_MSG0008
rows.name:
I want you to escort me to these coordinates
at sunset on a clear day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086701_MSG0009
rows.name: Sunset on a clear day, got it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086701_MSG0011
rows.name: You'll just have to go and find out.[ST:wait ]
